<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavaruṣaṁbulu 130<unclear>7</unclear> gunēṁṭi jyēṣṭa kṛṣṇa Ēkāda
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śi bhānuvārānaḍu <unclear>kau</unclear>ṁḍinyagō<unclear>tra</unclear> nārāya<supplied reason="omitted">ṇa</supplied>guruvu 
<lb n="3"/>pauvatra kriṣṇānaṁdaṁ saṁ<unclear>dhi</unclear>vigrahi bhāryya lakuvā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dēvi tanayu Abhīṣṭārtthasiddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>nāthuniki nityamunu Oka tirumāla ṟēpaṭi mā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>paṭi Avasarāna tātuṭaku numarppiṁcenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> I tō
<lb n="7" break="no"/>māla nityamunnu tecci veṭanu mādhavanāyumū
<lb n="8" break="no"/>lamaṁdu kōmaṭi lakume peṭaṁgalavāṁḍu śrībhaṁ
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḍāramaṁdu padmanidhigānu AIdu māḍālu sama
<lb n="10" break="no"/><unclear>rppiṁci kuṁcapra</unclear><supplied reason="omitted">sādamu</supplied> vṛttigāṁ bhaḍasi Itaniki cenu I pra
<lb n="11" break="no"/>sāda manubhaviṁci I tirumāla Ācaṁdrarkkastā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>Igā peṭṭaṁgalāṁḍu Ī dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava
<lb n="13"/>rakṣa śrī śrī śrī
</p>

